Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Terminal tabular data explorer
 tuitab is a fast, keyboard-driven terminal viewer for tabular data.
 It supports CSV, TSV, JSON, Parquet, Excel (xlsx/xls), and SQLite files.
 .
 Features include filtering, sorting, pivot tables, computed columns,
 column statistics, histograms and line/bar charts, transposing, and export.
 .
 The package provides three command names: tuitab, ttab, and tt.
